issue.title: Button formatting
issue.body: I need to be able to format each button according to the type it's supposed to be (add, up, down). Right now, the buttons in base.html have a consistent value and id, but those in search_results.html have a consistent name and value. However, we will need to remove the value soon in order to only show the image and not "Add", "Up", or "Down".  If you could decide whether I should use the name to determine the type of button or the id, that would be great.
